    dc:description "FIGURE 22. Species of Fusifilum Raf. displayed in horizontal rows of images. 1. Fusifilum capitatum (Hook.) Speta; 2. Fusifilum crenulatum U.M̧ll.-Doblies et al.; 3. Fusifilum depressum (Baker) U.M̧ll.-Doblies et al." ;
